{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Redstone Legal - Playful Justice</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c62828; /* A deep, playful red */\n            --secondary-color: #ef9a9a; /* A softer, complementary red */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --bg-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-bg: #f8f8f8;\n            --footer-bg: #f1f1f1;\n            --button-hover-bg: #b71c1c;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-bg);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-style: italic;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card {\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--bg-color);\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            color: var(--bg-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta p {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid transparent;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-bg);\n            color: var(--bg-color);\n            border-color: var(--bg-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-bg);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Redstone Legal</h1>\n            <p>Your partners in playful justice!</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>We believe that legal matters don't have to be stuffy or intimidating. At Redstone Legal, we bring a fresh, energetic approach to law, making the complex simple and the serious\u2026 well, a little less so. Our team is dedicated to providing top-notch legal services with a smile.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" style=\"background-color: var(--secondary-color); color: var(--bg-color);\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 style=\"color: var(--bg-color);\">Our Awesome Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-card\" style=\"background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-color); border-color: var(--brand-color);\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Shenanigans</h3>\n                    <p>Navigating the corporate jungle? We help businesses thrive with expert advice, from startup to IPO (and all the fun in between!).</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\" style=\"background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-color); border-color: var(--brand-color);\">\n                    <h3>Family Fun & Fairness</h3>\n                    <p>Handling sensitive family matters with care, compassion, and a touch of understanding. We aim for resolutions that make everyone happy (or at least, less grumpy).</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\" style=\"background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-color); border-color: var(--brand-color);\">\n                    <h3>Property Playgrounds</h3>\n                    <p>Buying, selling, or leasing property? We make real estate transactions smooth and straightforward, so you can focus on enjoying your space.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"feature-card\" style=\"background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-color); border-color: var(--brand-color);\">\n                    <h3>Dispute Resolution Disco</h3>\n                    <p>When disagreements arise, we're here to help you dance your way to a solution, whether through negotiation, mediation, or a bit of courtroom sparkle.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to make your legal life easier?</h2>\n            <p>Let's chat about how we can help you win your case (and maybe share a laugh or two!).</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get in Touch!</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>We're always here to lend an ear (and our legal expertise).</p>\n            <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@redstonelegal.com\">info@redstonelegal.com</a></p>\n            <p>Phone: <a href=\"tel:+1234567890\">(123) 456-7890</a></p>\n            <p>Visit our quirky office: 123 Redstone Lane, Playful City</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Redstone Legal. All rights reserved. Because justice should be fun!</p>\n            <p>Follow us on our adventures: <a href=\"#\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"#\">Facebook</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}